Hello All,
Referring to your email below of December 9.
Are you able to indicate the status of the undertaking of your independent =
investigations as proposed below.
We have received 3 tender responses back from the reinstatement service pro=
viders who attended site with Raffaella and myself late last year.
As we are all aware we have received these tender responses based on the sc=
ope of works provided by ASURNZ and subsequently shared with all parties.
Agreement on the scope of works is paramount to claim progression. If we ca=
n move to determine the agreed scope for claim related loss =E2=80=93 we ca=
n move quickly afterwards to provide the final outcome.
I look forward to an update on your independent enquiries.
Thank you very much.
Regards,
Grant.

