<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Good morning Raffae=
lla, Richard &amp; All,<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Please find attache=
d the following documents for your review:<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<ul type=3D"disc">
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mso-list:l4 level1 lfo2"><span lang=
=3D"FR" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Combustion pre-decontamination survey [ =
sent prior ]<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"=
mso-list:l4 level1 lfo2"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">ANZ1789 supplemen=
tary report<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"m=
so-list:l4 level1 lfo2"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Post fire structur=
al assessment report<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" s=
tyle=3D"mso-list:l4 level1 lfo2"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">ANZ1789 s=
cope of works [ revised &amp; updated ]<o:p></o:p></span></li></ul>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">The updated scope-o=
f-works attached has been created as a proposed inclusive response to the f=
indings of all the documents attached.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">While you are revie=
wing the attachments, I would like to propose that I begin the process of o=
btaining repair proposals from Tower approved builders to progress the clai=
m as quickly as possible.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">If I send out the s=
cope of works now and offer to meet with the tender respondents onsite, we =
may well have some preliminary costings to hand prior to the end of the bus=
iness year.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Please confirm your=
 approval for me to begin the process of preliminary pricing now.<o:p></o:p=
></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Best Regards,<o:p><=
/o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Grant.<o:p></o:p></=
span></p>
