<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-NZ"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Hi Stephen,<o:p></o=
:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Below is a copy of =
an email which I sent to all parties this afternoon outlaying the expected =
time frames of the results which will be available to be shared with all re=
garding test results from 23 Mays Street,
 Devonport.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></=
span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Prior to receiving =
the report from the forensic testing =E2=80=93 I am keen to take whatever s=
teps I can to progress the claim.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Preliminary results=
 and findings suggest that we may have a relatively complete understanding =
of what the final scope of works will be to fully remediate the property un=
der the claim.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></=
span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">If we accept on a p=
reliminary basis that the scope of works required to remediate the property=
 is
<b><u>generally defined</u></b> as follows:<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></=
span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><u><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Basement Level</=
span></u><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<ul type=3D"disc">
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mso-list:l0 level1 lfo3"><span styl=
e=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Clean and decontaminate all exposed internal brick s=
urfaces to ground level of dwelling<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoL=
istParagraph" style=3D"mso-list:l0 level1 lfo3"><span style=3D"font-size:11=
.0pt">Replace charred timber framework to midfloor structure and ground flo=
or walls as required<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" s=
tyle=3D"mso-list:l0 level1 lfo3"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Rebuild r=
ear deck and steps to match existing
<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mso-list:l0 =
level1 lfo3"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Replace all hardwood decking =
boards to internal balcony
<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mso-list:l0 =
level1 lfo3"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Clean and encapsulate all tim=
ber structural components to ground-floor walls and midfloor structure as r=
equired<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mso-l=
ist:l0 level1 lfo3"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Replace midfloor insul=
ation<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mso-lis=
t:l0 level1 lfo3"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Replace ceiling linings =
to ground floor as required<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParag=
raph" style=3D"mso-list:l0 level1 lfo3"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Su=
pply and install rear pedestrian door to rear of ground floor<o:p></o:p></s=
pan></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mso-list:l0 level1 lfo3"><=
span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Clean and repaint bi-folding basement doors=
 to ground floor<o:p></o:p></span></li></ul>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><u><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Second Level<o:p=
></o:p></span></u></p>
<ul type=3D"disc">
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mso-list:l10 level1 lfo4"><span sty=
le=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Disconnect, clean, and reinstall existing electrica=
l outlets and fittings as required<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoLi=
stParagraph" style=3D"mso-list:l10 level1 lfo4"><span style=3D"font-size:11=
.0pt">Remove all gib-board linings from the interior of the dwelling =E2=80=
=93
<u>exterior walls only [?]</u>. Ceilings to remain<o:p></o:p></span></li><l=
i class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mso-list:l10 level1 lfo4"><span style=
=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Clean and decontaminate all interior brick surfaces i=
n the exterior wall cavities<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListPara=
graph" style=3D"mso-list:l10 level1 lfo4"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">=
Encapsulate all timber framing to all exposed walls<o:p></o:p></span></li><=
li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mso-list:l10 level1 lfo4"><span styl=
e=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Re-line all exposed walls with new gib-board wall li=
nings. Gib-stop and sand to L4<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListPa=
ragraph" style=3D"mso-list:l10 level1 lfo4"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt=
">Seal and apply 2 topcoats to all new plasterboard linings<o:p></o:p></spa=
n></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mso-list:l10 level1 lfo4"><s=
pan style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Clean and repaint all remaining interior sur=
faces. Internal doors, exterior joinery, wardrobes, etc<o:p></o:p></span></=
li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mso-list:l10 level1 lfo4"><span =
style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Remove kitchen cabinetry as required to clean an=
d decontaminate any adjoining wall surfaces<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=
=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mso-list:l10 level1 lfo4"><span style=3D"fon=
t-size:11.0pt">Strip and refit entire bathroom to allow for decontamination=
 and remediation as required. Reuse existing fitting and fixtures where pos=
sible<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mso-lis=
t:l10 level1 lfo4"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Clean polished hardwood=
 strip flooring [ no re-coat of polyurethane ]<o:p></o:p></span></li></ul>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><u><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Roof Space</span=
></u><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<ul type=3D"disc">
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:-4.5pt;mso-list:l8 leve=
l1 lfo5"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Remove and replace all existing r=
oof insulation<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=
=3D"margin-left:-4.5pt;mso-list:l8 level1 lfo5"><span style=3D"font-size:11=
.0pt">Encapsulate all timber roof structure framing.<o:p></o:p></span></li>=
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:-4.5pt;mso-list:l8 leve=
l1 lfo5"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Remove and replace roofing underl=
ay paper<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"marg=
in-left:-4.5pt;mso-list:l8 level1 lfo5"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Re=
move, dispose of existing roof cladding<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"=
MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:-4.5pt;mso-list:l8 level1 lfo5"><spa=
n style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Supply and install new roofing cladding to mat=
ch existing<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"m=
argin-left:-4.5pt;mso-list:l8 level1 lfo5"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"=
>Supply and install new PVC spouting and downpipes<o:p></o:p></span></li><l=
i class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:-4.5pt;mso-list:l8 level1=
 lfo5"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Clean and repaint soffits<o:p></o:p=
></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:-4.5pt;mso=
-list:l8 level1 lfo5"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Clean and repaint fa=
scia board<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"ma=
rgin-left:-4.5pt;mso-list:l8 level1 lfo5"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">=
Supply and install new central heating unit to match existing =E2=80=93 or =
equivalent<o:p></o:p></span></li></ul>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><u><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">General<o:p></o:=
p></span></u></p>
<ul type=3D"disc">
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mso-list:l7 level1 lfo6"><span styl=
e=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Scaffold and shrink wrap dwelling to enable works<o:=
p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mso-list:l7 lev=
el1 lfo6"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Preliminary &amp; General works =
as required
<o:p></o:p></span></li></ul>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></=
span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I will need to disc=
uss the above with you in some detail, accepting that you may make correcti=
ons as required =E2=80=93 however once we have discussed the
<b><i><u>draft proposed scope</u></i></b> I will request that you provide T=
ower Insurance with a draft copy of the scope at which we arrive, and an ac=
companying cost estimate for reserving and quoting purposes.<o:p></o:p></sp=
an></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Let=E2=80=99s talk =
tomorrow when we can.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Many Thanks,<o:p></=
o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Grant. &nbsp;<o:p><=
